Task Manager - SOLID Architecture
[ [ [| Principle               | Implementation                                            |
| ----------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| S Single Responsibility | views.py (HTTP), services.py (Business), models.py (Data) |
| O Open/Closed           | Extensible TaskService & AuthService interfaces           |
| L Liskov Substitution   | Repository pattern - Django ORM ↔ Mock repos              |
| I Interface Segregation | ITaskRead vs ITaskWrite focused interfaces                |
| D Dependency Inversion  | Services depend on abstractions (ITaskRepository)         |
